tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE billing_and_insurance_claims_processing (
  consultation_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id UUID,
  consultation_date DATE,
  consultation_time TIME,
  billed_amount DECIMAL,
  insurance_claim_status VARCHAR
);

CREATE TABLE appointments (
    appointment_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id UUID NOT NULL,
    doctor_id UUID NOT NULL,
    appointment_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    status VARCHAR NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE insurance_claims (
    claim_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id UUID NOT NULL,
    appointment_id UUID NOT NULL,
    claim_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    amount DECIMAL NOT NULL,
    status VARCHAR NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE consultations (
  consultation_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT NOT NULL,
  psychiatrist_id INT NOT NULL,
  consultation_date DATE NOT NULL,
  consultation_duration INTERVAL NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE appointments (
  appointment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  appointment_date DATE,
  billing_code VARCHAR(10),
  consultation_fee DECIMAL(10, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE claims (
  claim_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  appointment_id INT,
  claim_date DATE,
  total_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
  status VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE Patients (
    patient_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    date_of_birth DATE,
    insurance_provider VARCHAR(50),
    insurance_policy_number VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE Consultations (
    consultation_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id UUID NOT NULL,
    psychiatrist_id UUID NOT NULL,
    consultation_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    consultation_duration INTERVAL NOT NULL
);
